üì± RESPONSIVE IMAGE HANDLING

Picture Element ‡∏™‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö Responsive Images

```blade
<picture>
    <!-- WebP format ‡∏™‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö browser ‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà support -->
    <source type="image/webp" 
            srcset="
                {{ asset('images/shopping/placeholders/product-small.webp') }} 80w,
                {{ asset('images/shopping/placeholders/product-medium.webp') }} 120w
            "
            sizes="(max-width: 768px) 80px, 120px">
    
    <!-- Fallback PNG -->
    <source type="image/png" 
            srcset="
                {{ asset('images/shopping/placeholders/product-small.png') }} 80w,
                {{ asset('images/shopping/placeholders/product-medium.png') }} 120w
            "
            sizes="(max-width: 768px) 80px, 120px">
    
    <!-- Fallback ‡∏´‡∏•‡∏±‡∏Å -->
    <img src="{{ asset('images/shopping/placeholders/product-medium.png') }}" 
         alt="{{ $product->name }}"
         loading="lazy">
</picture>
```

Lazy Loading Implementation

```blade
<img src="{{ $imageUrl }}" 
     alt="{{ $altText }}"
     loading="lazy"
     width="{{ $width }}"
     height="{{ $height }}"
     class="product-image">
```

